wdi-BX.GSR.GNFS.CD.def: Exports of goods and services comprise all transactions between residents of a country and the rest of the world involving a change of ownership from residents to nonresidents of general merchandise, net exports of goods under merchanting, nonmonetary gold, and services. Data are in current U.S. dollars.
wdi-BX.GSR.GNFS.CD.name: Exports of goods and services
wdi-BX.GSR.GNFS.CD.source: International Monetary Fund, Balance of Payments Statistics Yearbook and data files.
